title._content: Couple of people, better known as John Bennes and Ruth Glassow

description._content: Title: John Bennes with Ruth Glassow-0211201194311 Image Description: P.E. Director Ruth Glassow and Architect John V. Bennes standing on the steps of the Women's Building. Photo was used in the December 1926 OAC Alumnus, page 65. Original Collection: Harriet’s Collection Item Number: HC1514 You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here.
